OL,3,CPolice who shot man dead 'acted in
OL,4,Caccordance with training'
OL,6,FPolice officers who shot dead a man in
OL,7,FCarlisle 'acted in accordance with
OL,8,Ftheir training' according to the
OL,9,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,10,F(IOPC).
OL,12,FCumbria Constabulary firearms officers
OL,13,Fwere called to an address on Borland
OL,14,FAvenue around 3.30pm on Monday 19
OL,15,FDecember 2022. It had been reported
OL,16,Fthat a man was making threats to kill
OL,17,Fand young children were present.
OL,19,FOnce inside, the officers identified
OL,20,Fan imminent threat to a child and two
OL,21,Fofficers discharged their weapons.
