OL,3,CPolice who shot man dead 'acted in
OL,4,Caccordance with training'
OL,6,FSergii Kuzmenko, 40, suffered injuries
OL,7,Fto his head and chest and was
OL,8,Fpronounced dead at the scene.
OL,10,FThe investigation by the IOPC found
OL,11,Fthat seven shots were fired by two
OL,12,Fofficers. Both told investigators they
OL,13,Fwere acting under the belief there was
OL,14,Fan imminent threat to the child's life.
OL,16,FThe IOPC reviewed a large volume of
OL,17,Fevidence including accounts from
OL,18,Feleven Cumbria Constabulary officers,
OL,19,Fbody-worn camera footage and a report
OL,20,Ffrom a training expert in armed
OL,21,Fpolicing.
