OL,6,FThey concluded that the force used by
OL,7,Fofficers was in line with all relevant
OL,8,Ftraining and guidance.
OL,10,FIOPC Regional Director Catherine Bates
OL,11,Fsaid: "I would like to offer my
OL,12,Fsympathies to the family and friends
OL,13,Fof Mr Kuzmenko and everyone affected
OL,14,Fby this incident. It will have
OL,15,Fundoubtedly been a tremendously
OL,16,Fdifficult time and we appreciate their
OL,17,Fpatience and understanding while we
OL,18,Fhave carried out this very thorough
OL,19,Finvestigation.
