OL,6,F"I would also like to thank the
OL,7,Fofficers and staff involved for their
OL,8,Fcooperation with our investigation,
OL,9,Fduring what must also have been a very
OL,10,Fdifficult time for them.
OL,12,F"The evidence we gathered shows the
OL,13,Fofficers acted to protect a child
OL,14,Fwhose life they believed was in very
OL,15,Freal and immediate danger.
