OL,3,CPolice who shot man dead 'acted in
OL,4,Caccordance with training'
OL,6,F"The officers acted swiftly to gain
OL,7,Fentry to the room to prevent any
OL,8,Finjury to the child. We found the
OL,9,Fdecision to shoot Mr Kuzmenko was in
OL,10,Fline with all relevant training and
OL,11,Fguidance in those circumstances.
OL,13,F"While police shootings are,
OL,14,Fthankfully, rare it is understandable
OL,15,Fthat people will be concerned when it
OL,16,Fdoes happen and therefore it is
OL,17,Fimportant a detailed and robust
OL,18,Finvestigation is conducted to fully
OL,19,Funderstand the circumstances that led
OL,20,Fup to it."
